exports[`conditional writes — public contract acceptance local lock (friction hazard) fails loud with a caller-visible deadline message when a live lock never frees: live-lock-deadline 1`] = `
"UnexpectedCodePathError: could not acquire the local cache key lock within 5s — another writer holds it and did not release within the deadline.
this is expected only under heavy same-key write contention or a stuck writer.
to fix: retry the operation (transient contention clears on its own), or if a process crashed mid-write, delete the stale lock file at the lockPath below (it is auto-reclaimed after 30s).
the local tier is per-machine — for cross-machine coordination use the cloud (s3) tier."
`;

